text: Linthicum is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: * Hezekiah Linthicum Bateman (1812-1875), American actor and manager * John Charles Linthicum (1867-1932), Maryland politician * J. F. Linthicum, editor of Occidental and Vanguard *Lotta Linthicum (1870s-1952) American actress * Clayton Linthicum, Canadian guitarist and singer in Saskatchewan psych-folk- roots duo Kacy & Clayton.
